flowchart TD
    A[start_recording called] --> B[threading.Timer started\nmax_duration seconds default 300s]
    B --> C{Timer fires\nbefore user releases?}
    C -->|No — user releases first| D[Timer cancelled in stop_recording\n_max_duration_timer.cancel]
    C -->|Yes — max duration hit| E[_on_max_duration fires\ncall on_max_duration_reached callback]
    E --> F[TalkFlowApp._on_max_duration_reached\nprint ⏱️ Max recording duration reached]
    F --> G[call _stop_and_transcribe\nsame path as normal release]
    G --> H[proceeds through full\ntranscription and insertion flow]